column5: wow, first sime i have seen something like that before. Was there a price?
Saw this a little while ago on the board....  Someone said they called and asked what the interior or the RV looked like, and the reply was "A Boat".
Nautical decor seems dated but on the other hand, it accentuates the vintage of the motorhome.
..purchaser will need to obtain better tie-downs  :lol:
wonder what type of gas milage / top speed it gets on open water
